collection.description:
The First 10k Doge NFT Collection - Rediscovered by the Community! Among the First 10k NFT Collections on Ethereum (Created before BAYC - April 6th, 2021). Own a Piece of NFT History!

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/dooggies Website: https://dooggies.com/

1500 NFT's are reserved for the Community DAO. 100 for the Team, 400 for Giveaways.

The creator of Dooggies started learning programming at the age of 13 and created the Dooggies collection when he was 16 years old. 

Each Dooggie is represented as 32x32 pixel art NFT, programmatically assembled and scaled upward to 320x320 pixels. The Dooggies are stored as ERC 1155 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain, on an Opensea contract.

The NFT collection was revived and resurrected by NFT Archeologists in January 2022.

NFT collectors find this collection particularly noteworthy for the fact that it minted before BAYC and BAKC, yet it shares an overwhelming amount of traits with those collections.

Welcome to the Dooggies Family!
